comments: Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Booker's (PHX) path and continues to move into him, but Booker is able to go around it and continue playing defense.
Bridges (PHX) places a hand/arm to the front of Beal (WAS) during the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Bridges (PHX) makes clean contact to the ball first. Any additional contact to Beal (WAS) is incidental.
Beal (WAS) cleanly dislodges the ball from Booker (PHX).
Booker (PHX) maintains verticality when contesting Beal's (WAS) driving shot attempt.
Beal (WAS) maintains legal guarding position when contesting Booker's (PHX) shot attempt.
Parker (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bridges (PHX) and makes brief contact to Bridges' arm that does not affect his ability to defend.
During Beal's (WAS) drive, Beal makes marginal contact to Bridges (PHX) and does not affect his ability to defend.
Booker (PHX) is late to the spot and delivers contact to Satoransky (WAS) which affects his ability to defend.
Bryant (WAS) legally contests Crawford's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Holmes (PHX) makes contact to Bryant's (WAS) body during his shooting motion that affects his shot attempt.
Satoransky (WAS) briefly brings his hand around Ayton's (PHX) back but does not affect his FOM.
Green (WAS) legally contests Daniels' (PHX) jump shot attempt.
